&lt;li&gt;Create thumbnails in Photoshop.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Edit multi-camera projects in Adobe Premiere Pro.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understand audience data and implement appropriate changes to improve measurable results, such as thumbnail click-through rate and audience retention.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The strongest candidate will be data-driven, actively interested in modern poker content, and capable of developing ideas without needing every assignment fully mapped out in advance.&lt;/p&gt;
